column5: Hey, checking for info from some of u locals. Is the end of main landing open on the red up by netley? Now that they want 10 bucks a day in the park it would be nice to have another option

Its Open right now but i heard the waters low But justy wait it will rain or some other excuse and they will barricade the road again So if your coming up for the run Your guess is as good as ours around here Ps There has been some early signs of green already showing up
end of main is no prob launching your boat ....was there today...no dock...but ok to put boat in ...4 small walleye and a decent one ....plenty of drum....jeez ...and plenty of boats
end of main is ok to use. Decent fishing on the north part of the Red to boot.
